---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main class="prose mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-24">
    <h1>Refund &amp; Billing Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <p>CampSoon manages user value distribution transparently using a prepaid utility token infrastructure ($10 CAD equivalent package scale per 1,000 point increments).</p>

    <h3>1. Point Deductions &amp; Rendered Items</h3>
    <p>Each success milestone confirmed via browser notification tracking safely processes 1,000 points. Once assistance parameters fulfill and complete a spot mapping layout, the digital consumption is finalized and non-refundable.</p>

    <h3>2. 14-Day Vault Refund Window (Unused Tokens)</h3>
    <p>If you purchase any point bundle (Small, Standard, or Value) and maintain completely <strong>unused balances</strong>, you can request a 100% money-back refund on the transaction within 14 calendar days of your payment date.</p>

    <h3>3. Technical Errors &amp; System Discrepancies</h3>
    <p>If account point totals drop due to software logic error, false positive alert, or platform edge glitches without delivering camp location maps, send log receipts to our email for immediate point restoration or a full transaction reverse charge credit.</p>

    <h3>4. Contact Matrix</h3>
    <p>File clear intake requests to <strong>support@campsoon.com</strong> alongside valid payment receipts. Financial remits dispatch to initial card networks within 3-5 standard banking business days.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
